{"tid":1494662,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂牆-集中討論區 2","createTime":"2019-08-21T17:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T01:41:52.000Z","uid":125502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"863049510add39728f57922bdcdb13846558438f","tid":1494662,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:25:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連儂牆-集中討論區 2</span></strong><br />\n<strong>有關連儂牆各區想搵人幫手、突發事項、文宣投稿，都可以放喺度</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsqXxyU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsqXxyU.png&h=81b74205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n'<br />\n*最近都有其他嘢忙緊所以冇理到第一個post所以沉咗*<br />\n頭先好奇search一search，各適其適，天水圍、石籬、彩虹區乜都有<br />\n不如大家集中返同一個post，文宣都可以投稿係同一個集中post，避免其他活動post少咗人知道<br />\n題外話，今日行過先發現有阿伯完全唔知今日有721元朗活動，睇嚟需要再加強宣傳一啲<br />\n'<br />\n上一個post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1310435/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1310435/page/1</a><br />\n延伸閱讀：廣東歌文宣：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBPPbS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBPPbS</a>"},{"pid":"d6c644420512241993c5e0ba1e791d3d69aaa473","tid":1494662,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hsuEftH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhsuEftH.png&h=00a1416c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90o2dfo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90o2dfo.png&h=fea4058a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RiBWhG3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRiBWhG3.png&h=997cfc5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"806a4522809175a11b959196f2644999f35cb4c1","tid":1494662,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbQeJfn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbQeJfn